1289805161144092|title=Certificados Musicales Amprofon (Febrero 2019)|publisher=[[Asociaci\u00f3n Mexicana de Productores de Fonogramas y Videogramas]]|accessdate=July 8, 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* [[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|PROMUSICAE]]: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elportaldemusica.es/single/lele-pons-celoso|title=Lele Pons \u2013 Celoso|website=elportaldemusica.es|publisher=[[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a]]|accessdate=October 17, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"1\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Tel\u00e9fono|Tel\u00e9fono (Remix)]]\"<br />{{small|(with [[Aitana (singer)|Aitana]])}}\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 46 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 75\n|\n| ''[[Tr\u00e1iler]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bloqueo\"<br />{{small|(with [[Fuego (singer)|Fuego]])}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2019\n| 42 || \u2014 || 84 || 11 || \u2014 || 56\n|\n|rowspan=\"3\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Vete Pa La\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Volar\"<br />{{small|(feat. Susan Diaz and Victor Cardenas)}}\n|2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"14\" style=\"font-size:90%\" | \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| style=\"width:90%;\" class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Teen Choice Awards]]\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\"| Year\n! style=\"width:35%;\"| Nominated work\n! style=\"width:40%;\"| Category\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Result\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Herself\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Choice Viner\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2015\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Herself\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Choice Viner\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2015\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Herself\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Choice Web Sta